This is precisely what FundFantasy intends to do to the online trading market. Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Ecosystem FundFantasy:  Current Landscape: Since our platform and game is the first of its kind there are currently no active direct competitors. Our users share a common characteristic with users of the following platform types:  + Online Broker-Dealers  + Daily Fantasy Sports  + Online Poker Sites  + Online Casinos  + Online Lotteries  + Sports Betting Sites

Author: nikolayenko
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: FundFantasy is an online gaming platform FundFantasy is an online gaming platform featuring peer-to-peer, provably-fair simulated investing contests, where players compete for prizes under the fantasy model. By crafting the ultimate portfolio from a list of available assets, players move up in rank and win Crypto-prizes. Participants are ranked according to their portfolio’s rate of return. The prize pool is distributed among the winners. FundFantasy charges a fee which will not exceed 10% from each contest. Smart contracts will execute the whole process: deposits, ticket purchases, contests, payouts and withdrawals are all automated and trustless. Portfolios are encrypted to ensure fairness, and the entire platform is provably-fair and completely transparent.   Based on a deflationary currency and supported by an ecosystem that propels growth and new user acquisition , the FundFantasy platform will revolutionize the online trading market.

For example, if a participant has purchased 10% of the total amount of tokens sold, he will receive 10% of the tokens which were left undistributed when the token sale is finished. Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Hi there, excluding US citizens and institutions, anyone can participate! Thanks for the interest and welcome aboard!  Quote from: Ackedy on January 06, 2018, 06:20:16 AM Greetings! Whom do managers of the project consider to be their competitors? You know, there’re some traditional gaming platforms which gather gamers and money… Will they lure the games away from this start-up?  Quite the opposite! The gaming market is constantly looking for the next big thing. Take a look at Daily Fantasy Sports (DFS). 10 years ago, nobody believed in them at first, as sports betting was an already established market and was considered to be impenetrable. A decade later and people are reminded that a good product can change everything.  If anything, it's us that will lure the gamers away from other gaming platforms.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: 4 million tokens, which are 5% of the total token supply.  Quote from: jager44 on January 06, 2018, 08:23:13 AM Tell me please, what kinds of prizes will there be in contests? Will they be cash prizes, goods, any kinds of privileges or anything else?  Cryptocurrencies will be given as prizes to winners. These include FUNDZ, ETH, BTC, and perhaps other tokens in the future.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: A contest can be as short as 1 hour, but most investors would rather longer periods as it can allow their strategies to actually unfold. 8hrs (market session) has shown to be popular in our pilot, 24hrs also. There will be weekly, monthly and yearly contests as well!  With regards to restrictions, there are only the obvious ones (age, US citizens, verified users). Regardless of that - anyone can participate in both the ICO and the fantasy trading contests themselves.  Quote from: bit679 on January 06, 2018, 11:12:11 AM Hello! Tell me please, are there any prototypes or analogues of such a project in the traditional system? I’d like to learn about existing projects.  Yes! There is an alpha coming out very soon, check out the alpha thread: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2579397.new;topicseen#new  Shall we expect to see you there?

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Yes you're absolutely right, that's why we're working closely with law firms and gaming authorities. Currently it seems that the United States, although many states are open to the idea of Daily Fantasy Sports, will not be a market we target at first. Top lawyers say that there DEFINITELY ARE WAYS to operate in the US, perhaps not fully - we are in the process of securing legal opinions from leading legal firms in the Unites States and will update ASAP. Outside of the US we can operate in crypto wherever skill games are allowed, which is most of the world.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Good question - thanks! Many people who get into BTC start asking themselves "how do I make the profits I've been hearing of". Surfing a bit online they naturally get into alts and ICOs for chances at 10x or more. If they get better, they'll probably notice that our platform allows them to get 5x, 10x in one contest.  Nature doing its thing

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: I guess we will have to wait and see.  Quote from: Ackedy on January 08, 2018, 07:46:43 AM Quote from: MadduckUK on January 08, 2018, 07:41:28 AM Quote from: Ackedy on January 08, 2018, 07:28:41 AM Quote from: MadduckUK on January 08, 2018, 07:19:16 AM Quote from: Ackedy on January 08, 2018, 07:14:07 AM Quote from: MadduckUK on January 08, 2018, 07:08:28 AM Quote from: Ackedy on January 08, 2018, 07:02:30 AM Bless you, be wealthy! Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: The idea originated with Daniel Vaisman and Tal Zander two of FundFantasy's co-founders, both are online traders for over a decade. We think it's exciting too  Quote from: bars_kz on January 04, 2018, 11:11:09 PM Have a nice day! As for me, I’m confused by the fact that, for example, I’ve set a goal to work but investments but I will have just to play and struggle to become a winner. They often use the “fun” word in the WP. Of course it’s funny, but are there any preliminary estimations of the amount of people who will use such a platform? Are there any surveys?  This is a very good question indeed. There were a few attempts to gamify finance (but none were as intuitive as ours), and therefore there is not alot of data to learn from. For these reasons we have tested the model in a group of 100 testes and the responses were reassuring, as people were very excited and close to 50% said they would have played regularly if the platform was already online. To finish answering your question - FundFantasy targets online traders, amateur and professional alike, as well as gamers and fantasy sports users who have a financial touch, or would like to develop it in a fun environment.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: First let's make it clear that we believe in free markets. People should be able to go into voluntary interactions with each other, and should be able to choose what to do with their resources. No one should be able to tell anyone how to act - and people should protect their right to play.  Having said that, we do understand that speculation can lead to compulsive behaviour, which (especially if unprofitable) can wreak havoc in a man's life. For this reason we have adopted Responsible-Gaming policies - which allow users to limit their activity or completely self-exclude, whether temporarily or indefinitely.  Quote from: defender77 on January 05, 2018, 09:14:37 AM Greetings. What kind of problems and obstacles do developers see in the development of the project? Can anything hinder the development? In my opinion, the project balances on the thin line between real investment and gambling. [/quote]  Ask any experienced trader - every investment borders with gambling. The distinction is completely fictional. Both are speculative, stochastic, risky and done for a profit. That being said - unless the government completely shuts down the internet and the entire blockchain along with it, and unless they criminalize cryptocurrency, FundFantasy will be launched as expected.  It is possible however that certain jurisdictions will not allow us to operate within their borders, and we intend to comply with the relevant regulations in each jurisdictions.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Well it's pretty simple - you sign up, verify your account (easy), deposit (or join a free contest), choose a contests, create your portfolio, submit it - and watch the market go! If you win, you'll be notified and you'll see the prize added to your balance.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Currently we are just 10 days from launching the alpha, 20 days from the ICO! Phase I development is complete, we'll be adding features as we go. Official Launch is scheduled for Q3 2018.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: It depends on the asset: Data relating to stocks comes from the exchanges on which they are traded. Commodities are priced according to their nearest futures contact as received from the relevant markets.  In the case of crypto currencies - there may be differences between the prices of a coin in different exchanges. Depending on the coin we will disclose where the quote is taken from, and we'll be open to make changes in the quote sources according to necessity.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Good question; we do have ID verification and KYC on the platform, not only to ensure the legal age and to comply with AML, but also to preserve the fairness of the platform. As the platform gets more traction users will gain experience points and level up - new users should be able to play with users in the same level range and we will accomplish this by hosting contests which limit entry by user-level. This is another reason why we will maintain KYC, so that whales can't open new accounts and eat up all of the n00bs. Conclusion: Yes. There will be ID verification.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Thank you! Yes, the projects revolves around fantasy trading contests.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: In many jurisdictions skill games do not require licensing. Other jurisdictions will require licenses or legal opinions. We will comply with the regulatory framework of each jurisdiction we will operate in.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Another good question; we do have ID verification and KYC on the platform, not only to ensure the legal age and to comply with AML, but also to preserve the fairness of the platform and prevent users from opening multiple accounts. Conclusion: Yes, users will have to confirm their age, and users aren't allowed to use multiple accounts.

Body: Yes, users need to register and you must be 18+. Currently the platform runs on FundTokens, Ether and BTC. FundFantasy will allow the community to decide what additional Crytpocurrencies will be added. We are in the process of licensing in order to allow fiat currencies in the future.

Author: FundFantasy
Title: ✷[ENDED] 🌟FundFantasy🌟- FANTASY TRADING PLATFORM 🌟 🌟COMPLETED🌟🌟
Body: Thanks for the question! FundFantasy will not feature poker and or any other game aside from our simulated investing contests.  With regards to the airdrop and your inflation related worries - Our contest's smart contract will continuously and automatically burn 0.5% of every FUNDZ prize-pool on the platform. FundToken is a deflationary currency and the deflation will increase as the our platform grows and becomes a success. The airdrop is designed in such a way as to prevent the dilution of FUNDZ purchasers in relation to the team or the total market cap. Each participant will get more tokens if there are any tokens left unsold, and even thought its true that the price per token will decrease - participants in the ICO will retain the value of their investment.  Mathemathically speaking, our method is provably superior to the burning strategy, and should become standard practice in the world of ICO's  We will expand on the superiority of the airdrop compared to burning and how does it relate to the FundFantasy project in the upcoming days.
